# Agent Safety with Authensor

This project uses Authensor for agent safety. When working with agent tool calls:

1. Every tool call must go through Authensor policy evaluation
2. Use @authensor/engine for local evaluation or @authensor/sdk for control plane
3. Policies are in policy.yaml — edit rules there, not in code
4. Fail-closed: if no rule matches, the action is denied
5. High-risk actions should use effect: require_approval

Quick reference:
- Allow: safe read operations
- Deny: destructive operations, system file access
- Require approval: outbound communications, financial transactions

Docs: https://authensor.com/docs
